    #fb-root
    #fbloginpage(style='margin-left: 170px; margin-top: 10px')
      img(src='feedlearn-128px.png' style='position: absolute; left: 10px')
      h1 FeedLearn
      h3 Learn Japanese as you browse your Facebook news feed
      img(src='feedlearn-screenshot.png' style='border-radius: 15px')
      h3 Learn Japanese with FeedLearn!
      div FeedLearn is a Chrome extension that helps you learn Japanese vocabulary as you browse your Facebook feed.
      div If you would like to try FeedLearn, you can join our 3-week user study right now!
      //- div FeedLearn is a Chrome extension, so you must be using the Chrome browser. FeedLearn does not post to your wall or access any private data.
      div Each week, you will take a vocab test and learn 50 Japanese words with one of 3 tools.
      div To install FeedLearn and participate in the user study, please login below using Facebook (we do not post to your wall).
      div(style='padding-bottom: 10px')
      div.fb-login-button#fbloginbutton(data-max-rows='1' data-size='xlarge' data-show-faces='false' data-auto-logout-link='false' scope="public_profile,email" onlogin='fbButtonOnlogin()')
      div(style='padding-bottom: 10px')
      h3 Study Description
      div This is a research study to see whether we can help you learn Japanese vocabulary while browsing your Facebook news stream.
      div You will first install our Chrome extension, FeedLearn. This extension will show you vocabulary flashcards while you browse your Facebook news feed.
      div The study lasts for 3 weeks. Each week, you will:
      div(style='margin-left: 10px') 1) Take a vocab pre-test on the 50 new words you will be studying that week
      div(style='margin-left: 10px') 2) Study the words, using one of the following 3 approaches
      div(style='margin-left: 20px') • One week, you will be shown vocabulary quizzes directly in your feed
      div(style='margin-left: 20px') • Another week, you will be shown links in your feed asking you to go to the FeedLearn site to do the quizzes.
      div(style='margin-left: 20px') • Another week, you will be sent daily email reminders to study Japanese on the FeedLearn site.
      div(style='margin-left: 10px') 3) At the end of the week, you will take another vocabulary test to see what you have learned.
      div We do not access any of your private data or post anything on your Facebook wall. You can leave the study anytime.
      h3 Contact Information
      div If you have questions, ask 
        a(href='mailto:geza@cs.stanford.edu') Geza Kovacs

    #getfullname(style='margin-left: 10px; margin-top: 10px; display: none')
      div(style='font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 10px') Welcome to the FeedLearn study! What is your name?
